  "description": "A large, dark-hulled tanker ship is sailing on a calm, dark blue sea. The ship has a prominent red stripe along its hull and a tall, white and black superstructure with several antennas and a smokestack. In the background, a range of snow-capped mountains rises, partially obscured by fluffy white clouds. A coastal cityscape is faintly visible on the far left side of the frame, and a faint trail can be seen in the distance above the water. The sky is a mix of blue and white with diffused sunlight.",
